g-[var(--color-cream)]\" style=\"color:var(--color-ink)\" href=\"/courses/la\">LA</a><a class=\"px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded hover:bg-[var(--color-cream)]\" style=\"color:var(--color-ink)\" href=\"/courses/me\">ME</a><a class=\"px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded hover:bg-[var(--color-cream)]\" style=\"color:var(--color-ink)\" href=\"/courses/md\">MD</a><a class=\"px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded hover:bg-[var(--color-cream)]\" style=\"color:var(--color-ink)\" href=\"/courses/ma\">MA</a><a class=\"px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded hover:bg-[var(--color-cream)]\" style=\"color:var(--color-ink)\" href=\"/courses/mi\">MI</a><a class=\"px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded hover:bg-[var(--color-cream)]\" style=\"color:var(--color-ink)\" href=\"/courses/mn\">MN</a><a class=\"px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded hover:bg-[var(--color-cream)]\" style=\"color:var(--color-ink)\" href=\"/courses/ms\">MS</a><a class=\"px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded hover:bg-[var(--color-cream)]\" style=\"color:var(--color-ink)\" href=\"/courses/mo\">MO</a><a class=\"px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded hover:bg-[var(--color-cream)]\" style=\"color:var(--color-ink)\" href=\"/courses/mt\">MT</a><a class=\"px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded hover:bg-[var(--color-cream)]\" style=\"color:var(--color-ink)\" href=\"/courses/ne\">NE</a><a class=\"px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded hover:bg-[var(--color-cream)]\" style=\"color:var(--color-ink)\" href=\"/courses/nv\">NV</a><a class=\"px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded hover:bg-[var(--color-cream)]\" style=\"color:var(--color-ink)\" href=\"/courses/nh\">NH</a><a class=\"px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded hover:bg-[var(--color-cream)]\" style=\"color:var(--color-ink)\" href=\"/courses/nj\">NJ</a><a class=\"px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded hover:bg-[var(--color-cream)]\" style=\"color:var(--color-ink)\" href=\"/courses/nm\">NM</a><a class=\"px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded hover:bg-[var(--color-cream)]\" style=\"color:var(--color-ink)\" href=\"/courses/ny\">NY</a><a class=\"px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded hover:bg-[var(--color-cream)]\" style=\"color:var(--color-ink)\" href=\"/courses/nc\">NC</a><a class=\"px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded hover:bg-[var(--color-cream)]\" style=\"color:var(--color-ink)\" href=\"/courses/nd\">ND</a><a class=\"px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded hover:bg-[var(--color-cream)]\" style=\"color:var(--color-ink)\" href=\"/courses/oh\">OH</a><a class=\"px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded hover:bg-[var(--color-cream)]\" style=\"color:var(--color-ink)\" href=\"/courses/ok\">OK</a><a class=\"px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded hover:bg-[var(--color-cream)]\" style=\"color:var(--color-ink)\" href=\"/courses/or\">OR</a><a class=\"px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded hover:bg-[var(--color-cream)]\" style=\"color:var(--color-ink)\" href=\"/courses/pa\">PA</a><a class=\"px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded hover:bg-[var(--color-cream)]\" style=\"color:var(--color-ink)\" href=\"/courses/ri\">RI</a><a class=\"px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded hover:bg-[var(--color-cream)]\" style=\"color:var(--color-ink)\" href=\"/courses/sc\">SC</a><a class=\"px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded hover:bg-[var(--color-cream)]\" style=\"color:var(--color-ink)\" href=\"/courses/sd\">SD</a><a class=\"px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded hover:bg-[var(--color-cream)]\" style=\"color:var(--color-ink)\" href=\"/courses/tn\">TN</a><a class=\"px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded hover:bg-[var(--color-cream)]\" style=\"color:var(--color-ink)\" href=\"/courses/tx\">TX</a><a class=\"px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded hover:bg-[var(--color-cream)]\" style=\"color:var(--color-ink)\" href=\"/courses/ut\">UT</a><a class=\"px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded hover:bg-[var(--color-cream)]\" style=\"color:var(--color-ink)\" href=\"/courses/vt\">VT</a><a class=\"px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded hover:bg-[var(--color-cream)]\" style=\"color:var(--color-ink)\" href=\"/courses/va\">VA</a><a class=\"px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded hover:bg-[var(--color-cream)]\" style=\"color:var(--color-ink)\" href=\"/courses/wa\">WA</a><a class=\"px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded hover:bg-[var(--color-cream)]\" style=\"color:var(--color-ink)\" href=\"/courses/wv\">WV</a><a class=\"px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded hover:bg-[var(--color-cream)]\" style=\"color:var(--color-ink)\" href=\"/courses/wi\">WI</a><a class=\"px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded hover:bg-[var(--color-cream)]\" style=\"color:var(--color-ink)\" href=\"/courses/wy\">WY</a><a class=\"px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded hover:bg-[var(--color-cream)]\" style=\"color:var(--color-ink)\" href=\"/courses/dc\">DC</a></div></div></details><a class=\"hover:text-[var(--color-evergreen-950)] transition-colors\" href=\"/search\">Search</a><a class=\"hover:text-[var(--color-evergreen-950)] transition-colors\" href=\"/near-me\">Near me</a><a href=\"https://opengolfapi.org/#api\" class=\"hover:text-[var(--color-evergreen-950)] transition-colors\">API</a><a class=\"px-3 py-1.5 rounded text-sm font-semibold\" style=\"background:var(--color-evergreen-950);color:var(--color-cream)\" href=\"/submit\">Submit</a></div></nav></header><main class=\"flex-1\"><div class=\"max-w-[760px] mx-auto px-6 pt-12 pb-16\"><p class=\"font-display italic text-[15px] mb-3\" style=\"color:var(--color-brass-700);font-variation-settings:&quot;opsz&quot; 14\">The fine print, in plain English</p><h1 class=\"font-display tracking-tight font-bold mb-4\" style=\"font-size:clamp(36px, 5vw, 60px);line-height:1.05\">Terms of<!-- --> <em style=\"color:var(--color-brass-700);font-style:italic\">service.</em></h1><p class=\"text-lg mb-3 max-w-[640px]\" style=\"color:var(--color-ink-muted)\">OpenGolfAPI is a community-maintained open dataset of US golf courses, with an optional REST API and MCP server on top. By using any of it, you&#x27;re agreeing to what&#x27;s below.</p><p class=\"text-sm mb-12\" style=\"color:var(--color-ink-muted)\">Last updated: <!-- -->2026-05-03</p><section class=\"mb-10\"><p class=\"font-display italic text-[13px] mb-2\" style=\"color:var(--color-brass-700);font-variation-settings:&quot;opsz&quot; 14\">What you’re using</p><h2 class=\"font-display font-bold mb-3\" style=\"font-size:clamp(22px, 2.4vw, 28px);line-height:1.15\">The service.</h2><div class=\"text-[16px] space-y-4\" style=\"color:var(--color-ink)\"><p>OpenGolfAPI provides a free open dataset of US golf courses (geometry, tees, scorecards, hazards, and metadata), plus optional access via a REST API and an MCP server for AI agents. The dataset and tooling are operated by an unincorporated solo maintainer (“we,” “us”) — not a registered company.</p></div></section><section class=\"mb-10\"><p class=\"font-display italic text-[13px] mb-2\" style=\"color:var(--color-brass-700);font-variation-settings:&quot;opsz&quot; 14\">The data is yours</p><h2 class=\"font-display font-bold mb-3\" style=\"font-size:clamp(22px, 2.4vw, 28px);line-height:1.15\">License.</h2><div class=\"text-[16px] space-y-4\" style=\"color:var(--color-ink)\"><p>All course data is published under the<!-- --> <a href=\"https://opendatacommons.org/licenses/odbl/1-0/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" class=\"underline\">Open Data Commons Open Database License (ODbL) 1.0</a>. You can download it, redistribute it, and build commercial products on top of it. Attribution is required: cite<!-- --> <strong style=\"color:var(--color-ink)\">“OpenGolfAPI, ODbL”</strong> <!-- -->wherever the data shows up.</p><p>ODbL is a copyleft data license — derivative databases must be shared under the same terms. Read the full license text if you plan to redistribute.</p></div></section><section class=\"mb-10\"><p class=\"font-display italic text-[13px] mb-2\" style=\"color:var(--color-brass-700);font-variation-settings:&quot;opsz&quot; 14\">Rate limits</p><h2 class=\"font-display font-bold mb-3\" style=\"font-size:clamp(22px, 2.4vw, 28px);line-height:1.15\">API usage.</h2><div class=\"text-[16px] space-y-4\" style=\"color:var(--color-ink)\"><p>The API is free at every tier. Limits exist so one user can&#x27;t starve everyone else:</p><ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 space-y-1.5\"><li><strong style=\"color:var(--color-ink)\">Anonymous:</strong> <!-- -->1,000 requests per day, per IP.</li><li><strong style=\"color:var(--color-ink)\">Keyed (free):</strong> <!-- -->10,000 requests per day, per key.</li><li><strong style=\"color:var(--color-ink)\">Higher tiers:</strong> <!-- -->available with a recurring donation via<!-- --> <a href=\"https://opencollective.com/opengolfapi\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" class=\"underline\">Open Collective</a>.</li></ul><p>Limits are enforced. Sustained abuse — scraping past limits, rotating IPs to dodge the cap, or any pattern that looks like a denial-of-service attempt — may result in your key being revoked without notice.</p></div></section><section class=\"mb-10\"><p class=\"font-display italic text-[13px] mb-2\" style=\"color:var(--color-brass-700);font-variation-settings:&quot;opsz&quot; 14\">Best effort</p><h2 class=\"font-display font-bold mb-3\" style=\"font-size:clamp(22px, 2.4vw, 28px);line-height:1.15\">No SLA.</h2><div class=\"text-[16px] space-y-4\" style=\"color:var(--color-ink)\"><p>OpenGolfAPI is community-maintained, best-effort. There is no uptime guarantee, no support contract, and no obligation on us to keep any specific endpoint, schema, or behavior stable forever.</p><p><strong style=\"color:var(--color-ink)\">Do not use this service for life-critical or safety-critical applications.</strong> <!-- -->Don&#x27;t use it to navigate, to make medical decisions, to control equipment, or for anything where a wrong answer or an outage could hurt someone.</p></div></section><section class=\"mb-10\"><p class=\"font-display italic text-[13px] mb-2\" style=\"color:var(--color-brass-700);font-variation-settings:&quot;opsz&quot; 14\">As-is</p><h2 class=\"font-display font-bold mb-3\" style=\"font-size:clamp(22px, 2.4vw, 28px);line-height:1.15\">No warranties.</h2><div class=\"text-[16px] space-y-4\" style=\"color:var(--color-ink)\"><p>The service and the data are provided <em>as-is</em>, with all faults, and without warranty of any kind — express, implied, or statutory. We disclaim, to the maximum extent permitted by law, any warranty of merchantability, fitness for a particular purpose, accuracy, completeness, non-infringement, and quiet enjoyment.</p><p>You assume all risk associated with your use.</p></div></section><section class=\"mb-10\"><p class=\"font-display italic text-[13px] mb-2\" style=\"color:var(--color-brass-700);font-variation-settings:&quot;opsz&quot; 14\">The cap</p><h2 class=\"font-display font-bold mb-3\" style=\"font-size:clamp(22px, 2.4vw, 28px);line-height:1.15\">Liability.</h2><div class=\"text-[16px] space-y-4\" style=\"color:var(--color-ink)\"><p>To the maximum extent permitted by law, our aggregate liability to you for any and all claims arising out of or relating to this service — regardless of the legal theory (contract, tort, negligence, strict liability, statute, or otherwise) — is capped at<!-- --> <strong style=\"color:var(--color-ink)\">USD $100</strong>.</p><p>We are not liable for indirect, incidental, special, consequential, exemplary, or punitive damages, lost profits, lost data, or business interruption, even if we&#x27;ve been advised that such damages were possible.</p></div></section><section class=\"mb-10\"><p class=\"font-display italic text-[13px] mb-2\" style=\"color:var(--color-brass-700);font-variation-settings:&quot;opsz&quot; 14\">Keys are revocable</p><h2 class=\"font-display font-bold mb-3\" style=\"font-size:clamp(22px, 2.4vw, 28px);line-height:1.15\">Termination.</h2><div class=\"text-[16px] space-y-4\" style=\"color:var(--color-ink)\"><p>We may revoke any API key at any time, for any reason, including (but not limited to) abuse, fraud, suspected fraud, security concerns, or operational reasons. Where practical we&#x27;ll email you first; where it isn&#x27;t, we won&#x27;t.</p><p>You can stop using the service whenever you like. To delete your key and the email tied to it, write to<!-- --> <a href=\"mailto:hello@opengolfapi.org\" class=\"underline\">hello@opengolfapi.org</a>.</p></div></section><section class=\"mb-10\"><p class=\"font-display italic text-[13px] mb-2\" style=\"color:var(--color-brass-700);font-variation-settings:&quot;opsz&quot; 14\">Don’t do these things</p><h2 class=\"font-display font-bold mb-3\" style=\"font-size:clamp(22px, 2.4vw, 28px);line-height:1.15\">Acceptable use.</h2><div class=\"text-[16px] space-y-4\" style=\"color:var(--color-ink)\"><p>You agree not to:</p><ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 space-y-1.5\"><li>Attempt to overload, degrade, or disrupt the service.</li><li>Resell or redistribute raw data without the required ODbL attribution.</li><li>Use the service or the data to harass, threaten, or defame course owners, operators, staff, or other contributors.</li><li>Submit fraudulent edits, fake claims, or deliberately wrong data.</li><li>Use the service to violate any applicable law or third-party right.</li></ul></div></section><section class=\"mb-10\"><p class=\"font-display italic text-[13px] mb-2\" style=\"color:var(--color-brass-700);font-variation-settings:&quot;opsz&quot; 14\">These will change</p><h2 class=\"font-display font-bold mb-3\" style=\"font-size:clamp(22px, 2.4vw, 28px);line-height:1.15\">Changes to these terms.</h2><div class=\"text-[16px] space-y-4\" style=\"color:var(--color-ink)\"><p>We may update these terms from time to time. The “Last updated” date at the top of this page is the source of truth. Material changes — anything that meaningfully affects your rights or obligations — will be emailed to keyed users at the address on file.</p><p>Continued use of the service after a change means you accept it.</p></div></section><section class=\"mb-10\"><p class=\"font-display italic text-[13px] mb-2\" style=\"color:var(--color-brass-700);font-variation-settings:&quot;opsz&quot; 14\">Where this lives</p><h2 class=\"font-display font-bold mb-3\" style=\"font-size:clamp(22px, 2.4vw, 28px);line-height:1.15\">Governing law.</h2><div class=\"text-[16px] space-y-4\" style=\"color:var(--color-ink)\"><p>These terms are governed by the laws of the United States and applicable federal law. Any dispute is subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of US federal and state courts.</p></div></section><section class=\"mb-10\"><p class=\"font-display italic text-[13px] mb-2\" style=\"color:var(--color-brass-700);font-variation-settings:&quot;opsz&quot; 14\">Last thing</p><h2 class=\"font-display font-bold mb-3\" style=\"font-size:clamp(22px, 2.4vw, 28px);line-height:1.15\">Contact.</h2><div class=\"text-[16px] space-y-4\" style=\"color:var(--color-ink)\"><p>Questions about these terms, requests to delete your account, or anything that doesn&#x27;t fit a form go to<!-- --> <a href=\"mailto:hello@opengolfapi.org\" class=\"underline\">hello@opengolfapi.org</a>. One person reads every email.</p></div></section></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"border-t mt-20 px-6 py-12\" style=\"border-color:var(--color-cream-darkest);color:var(--color-ink-muted)\"><div class=\"max-w-[1100px] mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 text-sm mb-8\"><div><h4 class=\"font-display text-base font-semibold mb-3\" style=\"color:var(--color-ink)\">OpenGolfAPI</h4><p class=\"mb-2\">An open almanac of American golf.</p><span class=\"inline-block text-[11px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full font-semibold tracking-wider\" style=\"background:var(--color-cream-darker);color:var(--color-ink)\">ODbL 1.0</span></div><div><h4 class=\"font-display text-base font-semibold mb-3\" style=\"color:var(--color-ink)\">Browse</h4><a class=\"block py-0.5 hover:text-[var(--color-evergreen-950)]\" href=\"/\">All courses</a><a class=\"block py-0.5 hover:text-[var(--color-evergreen-950)]\" href=\"/search\">Search</a><a class=\"block py-0.5 hover:text-[var(--color-evergreen-950)]\" href=\"/near-me\">Near me</a><a class=\"block py-0.5 hover:text-[var(--color-evergreen-950)]\" href=\"/submit\">Submit a course</a><a class=\"block py-0.5 hover:text-[var(--color-evergreen-950)]\" href=\"/my-edits\">My contributions</a></div><div><h4 class=\"font-display text-base font-semibold mb-3\" style=\"color:var(--color-ink)\">Build</h4><a href=\"https://opengolfapi.org/#api\" class=\"block py-0.5 hover:text-[var(--color-evergreen-950)]\">API docs</a><a class=\"block py-0.5 hover:text-[var(--color-evergreen-950)]\" href=\"/pricing\">Pricing</a><a class=\"block py-0.5 hover:text-[var(--color-evergreen-950)]\" href=\"/api-keys\">Get an API key</a><a href=\"https://github.com/opengolfapi\" class=\"block py-0.5 hover:text-[var(--color-evergreen-950)]\">GitHub</a><a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/@opengolfapi/mcp-server\" class=\"block py-0.5 hover:text-[var(--color-evergreen-950)]\">MCP server</a></div><div><h4 class=\"font-display text-base font-semibold mb-3\" style=\"color:var(--color-ink)\">Support</h4><a href=\"https://opencollective.com/opengolfapi\" class=\"block py-0.5 hover:text-[var(--color-evergreen-950)]\">Donate</a><a class=\"block py-0.5 hover:text-[var(--color-evergreen-950)]\" href=\"/contact\">Contact</a><a href=\"https://github.com/opengolfapi/opengolfapi/issues\" class=\"block py-0.5 hover:text-[var(--color-evergreen-950)]\">Report an issue</a><a class=\"block py-0.5 hover:text-[var(--color-evergreen-950)]\" href=\"/status\">Status</a><a class=\"block py-0.5 hover:text-[var(--color-evergreen-950)]\" href=\"/legal/privacy\">Privacy</a><a class=\"block py-0.5 hover:text-[var(--color-evergreen-950)]\" href=\"/legal/terms\">Terms</a></div></div><p class=\"max-w-[1100px] mx-auto pt-6 text-center text-xs border-t\" style=\"border-color:var(--color-cream-darkest)\">Data licensed under <a href=\"https://opendatacommons.org/licenses/odbl/1-0/\" class=\"underline\">ODbL 1.0</a> · Booking links are affiliate — we may earn a small commission at no cost to you.</p></footer><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0hvu8ydxmxc5p.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[79520,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/001b~5_czkb82.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/ch